{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
If Black extends from the top at 1 then White will capture Black with 2 and 4.  Black doesn't have a good next move.

This diagram is a big loss for Black.  The corner is forfeit, White gains a very strong group, and goes to show you when we don't know how to correctly respond we end up losing big.
